data.description: ASSUMABLE 3.75% VA LOAN!! Come experience the Satellite Beach Lifestyle! Completely Remodeled inside and out! Your new Backyard Oasis is calling. With stunning upgrades throughout, this home sits in the heart of Satellite Beach on a corner lot surrounded by mature Royal Palms and a fenced in yard. Conveniently just blocks from everything your family will enjoy from the library, Soccer/football fields, Playground, Skatepark, and city manned Dog park your pup will love! As you move inside you will notice the all the upgrades. From top of the line luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout to the stainless steel appliances and all new fixtures. A mixture of the mature trees and the Brand New Floor to Ceiling Hurricane Impact Windows provides the perfect serene natural light in your open concept living room and kitchen. Metal Roof (2019) AC (2017). A Built in Putting Green in the back yard?! Practice your putts while watching TV next to your Oversized POOL surrounded with pavers.
